h3. Summary

Service Desk customers can't access public Confluence pages.

h3. Steps to Reproduce
# Create an user with access 'Restricted Portal';
# Create a space in Confluence;
# Set Anonymous access on the space (Space tools);
# Try accessing the homepage of the space (created on step 3) using the user 'Restricted Portal' (created on step 2);

h3. Expected Results

The user with 'Restricted Portal' should see the page assuming that it is open for all kind of users.

h3. Actual Results

{noformat}

Not Permitted
You are not permitted to perform this operation.
{noformat}
 If the user opens the space using a incognito window, the pages is shown.

