h3. Summary
Users can’t save a page when inserting a date on the day when Daylight Saving Time starts

h3. Steps to Reproduce 
# Check the default time zone of the instance {{Asia/Beirut}}
# Verify when the Daylight Saving Time starts on that timezone {{2016-03-27}}
# Try to edit a page insert date {{2016-03-27}}
# The page can't be saved with error {{There was an error processing the request}}

h3. Expected Results
Should be able to save the page after inserting the date.

h3. Actual Results
{{There was an error processing the request}} error will appear when saving the page. 

